description.en:
FNX token has an array of benefits that make it the must have token as we
approach in the future:

- Trading fees are discounted .

- FNX token creates its own market, paired with every coin and every local currency on the FinanceX exchange. FNX oers easy access to the market and favoring high liquidity.

- FinanceX will already have two functioning exchanges when FNX token is listed with enormous population bases tapped into. The creation of an inter-exchange network supporting local currency means FNX will be directly exposed to new markets with new investors on a consistent basis.

- FNX token is not only used for business purpose but also entertainment. You can spend FNX to join the games to earn more assets and prots as well.

- Joining many events with FNX can help you increase your Xpoint. Xpoint will be used as loyalty point to enjoy other benets of FinanceX in the future.
